						<summary>

						<p>Stone on the way to Penikalapāḍu.</p>						

						<p>It states that the land near the boundary between Nallapalle and Penikalapādu belongs to the artisan Rāchabhattudu of Vēlupujla(jarla). In late characters.</p>						

